reviewText: A comedy that will live on for ages

Came quickly and is excellent quality. We love this movie! We quote it all the time.  I bought this to show to a couple of my friends who have never seen the movie. It is so funny! Steve Carell is hilarious!
this movie is hilarious. a friend of mine and i quote it all the time
Movie is super funny. Too bad this Blu-ray copy only came with one disk, no instant access online or has a digital version included.
Very funny, will never have to watch the version on TV again

I was excited when it arrived although it took a while, but considering it came from really far I did not have a problem with it. The movies where exactly like I wanted them and they also had an option to view in French.
